sec.p:
The objective is to run a definitive multi-centre pragmatic RCT testing the clinical and cost-effectiveness of the SPHERe intervention compared to best-practice usual care, including:
A pre-pilot to test feasibility, refine intervention delivery and manualised practitioner training, and prepare trial set-up at selected centres;
An internal pilot, with formative process evaluation, at a sample of out-patient centres to test recruitment and trial procedures;
A main trial with embedded process evaluation.
